body:
What is this game and what is it for?
I am really curious to find out people's opinions on me. So for fun I am making a little game for it!

How to play:
So first of all give your full opinion on the person above you.
This is optional, but you can give your full opinion on me

PLEASE DON'T BE RUDE OR START A FLAME WAR! THIS IS FOR FUN!

I'll start, I guess I have to give my opinions on myself...

Tynvale: From what I have seen you're an absolute g0d. Some even call you a Future Savage and I agree, I really like your great looks and I love talking to you on TS! I am big sub on your Youtube and I see you getting to 10 subs any day now, I am still quite emotional about the restart but I understand <3
